description: Streetside Sushi is rolling through the streets of Detroit and serving up some sensational Japanese cuisine. With a mission to provide fresh and healthy sushi to all the local foodies, the Streetside team has crafted a delicious selection of miso soup, California rolls, spicy shrimp tempura rolls, tuna rolls, etc...For all this and more, stop on by Streetside Sushi!
name: Streetside Sushi
